                                text="&lt;p>&lt;span class=&quot;light-font&quot;>&lt;span class=&quot;body-unica-32-reg&quot;> Through a decade-long partnership, AMPATH and the AbbVie Foundation empower expectant mothers in Kenya through health and microfinancing education&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;"
